<item>
            <title>[SPARK-49852] Fix deadlock between shuffle dependency initialization and explain string generation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-49852</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We hit a deadlock between shuffle dependency initialization and explain string generation, in which both code paths trigger lazy variable instantiation while visiting some tree nodes in different orders and thus acquiring object locks in a reversed order.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The hashcode of plan node is implemented as lazy val. So the fix is to remove hash code computation from explain string generation so to break the chain of lazy variable instantiation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
